Script,JacobySuperAccept
setDealerCode(`

# Import Define-1N and Calm Opponents
Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/Define-1N
Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/Calm-Opponents

# Define North's Jacoby Transfer and South's Super Accept (not Smolen)
nSps = spades(north)>5 and spades(south)>3 and hearts(north)<4 and hcp(north)<10
nHps = hearts(north)>5 and hearts(south)>3 and spades(north)<4 and hcp(north)<10
nSgf = spades(north)==5 and spades(south)>3 and hearts(north)<4 and hcp(north)>9
nHgf = hearts(north)==5 and hearts(south)>3 and spades(north)<4 and hcp(north)>9

# Now OPEN 1NT
NT and (nSps or nHps or nSgf or nHgf) and calmWest

# Generate Statistics
action
average "Heart Fit" 100 * nH,
average "Spade Fit" 100 * nS, 

`,"S",true)
Script
Button,Jacoby Super-Accept,\n\
---  Jacoby Super-Accept\n\
South opens 1N w/2452+2425+2245+2254+4522 or any 4333，4432，or 5332 distribution.\n\
Those 5422 hands are the ones where you are likely to have to reverse to show your suits.\n\
HCP adjusted +1 for any 5-card suit unless you have Kx，Qx，or Jx doubleton.\n\
North transfers to Hearts or Spades and South has 4- or 5-card support.\n\
%JacobySuperAccept%